\caption{(A) The distance-dependent crosscorrelation function $\phi(r)$ averaged for proteins with similar $R_g$. 
(B) Scattering plot of correlation length $\xi_\phi$ as a function of the average $R_g$, where the red symbols  show the average $\xi= f(R_g)$ with the error bars denoting the standard deviation. 
